dc_title_s: Comitatus Legeniae: The countie of Leinster; Amstelodami, Apud Joannem Janssonium.; Comitatvs Legeniae: The covntie of Leinster
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Map is oriented with North to the right. Includes drawings of ships in the ocean. This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637, and 1680. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map: 37 x 48 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
